manifests.contents:
bench = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "hailmary"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[[test]]
path = "tests/finalytics_tests.rs"
name = "finalytics_tests"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[[test]]
path = "tests/profile_tests.rs"
name = "profile_tests"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "hailmary"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.89"
axum = "0.6"
chrono = "0.4.38"
dotenvy = "0.15.7"
serde_json = "1.0"
thiserror = "1.0.64"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.6"
features = ["runtime-tokio-native-tls", "postgres", "uuid", "json"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.28"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.11.0"
features = ["v4"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "hailmary"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]

[profile.dev.package.sqlx-macros]
opt-level = 3
